{"tid":165590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毒霧橫行 陝西一罐空氣賣18元人民幣","createTime":"2017-03-21T12:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T03:07:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b49b518d608995d798a1e7ffdb317d1557ef742","tid":165590,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"2017年03月20日 20:44<br />\n一罐空氣值多少錢？對於大多數人來說，這可能是一個無厘頭的問題。然而，在陝西省街頭，這個答案是&mdash;&mdash;18元人民幣，約81元新台幣。<br />\n<br />\n紅星新聞網報導，在西安兩家土特產展銷中心的貨架上，出現一種特殊的商品：空氣。這些空氣被灌裝起來，每罐750ml，市場售價18元。<br />\n<br />\n這些罐裝空氣是由陝西省寧東林業局出品。面對民眾的質疑，陝西寧東林業局產業發展科科長郭林文說，這是一款旅遊紀念品，是森林公園的土特產。以前西安毒霧嚴重，好多人來森林公園吸氧，因此就想可以賣空氣。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170320005632-260409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170320005632-260409&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6d6c57f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170320005632-260409</a>"},{"pid":"7ae68aeb51313f2dc9360602fc2f0e5124f98d9c","tid":165590,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ee77e98b5d8d4d8f1561fcb7c3c1866693836b","tid":165590,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"畀錢買支那毒氣"},{"pid":"121f220cd6ea88cfb997b0805a824d58ecab2b87","tid":165590,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"瑞士山區肺有得諗"},{"pid":"8a4561d41519329c57ac6221cee36c50135679bf","tid":165590,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瑞士山區肺有得諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n換湯不換藥"},{"pid":"fb0d1bd6f417f1621c0ced4e71402a9d694b065e","tid":165590,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dd93975fdae8ddf3d8da12a3091a2a13565345","tid":165590,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:41:09.000Z","msg":"看錯成&quot;毒撚橫行&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3debb547aa333c8daf6f151e23ff4b348ad7a42b","tid":165590,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d41e9ef3f35e61709a9044a340bcc8dcbf58d9","tid":165590,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T02:53:14.000Z","msg":"罐裡面咪又係毒氣 會俾真野你咩"},{"pid":"e4f8734379db20b62bf2ddb97efd0d73dc0e003c","tid":165590,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:07:11.000Z","msg":"強國人有錢到唔吸免費空氣，地球貴族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}